{"tid":2457453,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個放工後唔再諗公事嘅方法，好高壓，想完全switch off","createTime":"2021-03-22T15:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T09:56:48.000Z","uid":323520,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"47fe449899b8a862f3a226f85664bbe9de323ad7","tid":2457453,"uid":323520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T15:48:42.000Z","msg":"見到有d同事工作時好投入，但<br />\n一放工就可以完全switch off，好似熄左機咁，日頭返工個人就開返機咁，明明大家嘅工作環境都一樣咁高壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪我渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩方法可以放工/放假就完全放低工作嘅野唔諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過胃痛，失眠，發惡夢，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補充返少少background info<br />\n大公司 做admin 要管人<br />\n大老細好chur 長期處於高壓狀態<br />\n最近發現開始頂唔順<br />\n但唔會貿貿然轉工<br />\n想努力克服<br />\n巴絲們有無好方法可以教下路<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想擺脫成日諗公事嘅壞習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92957689723a4a566a521ccba92ce03c0b9c4d9c","tid":2457453,"uid":50521,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"做運動，真係幾好，出身汗，我都一樣，但唔係公司，唔係壓力，只係個人好灰，成日都好唔開心禁，所以成日做下運動，做做下就唔會諗禁多野。"},{"pid":"8604f24bab4fc70f216e4e88dc142ed4e3c3fbeb","tid":2457453,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T16:02:15.000Z","msg":"做運動..."},{"pid":"cf3741f6da842b965100dc0d3831781847e53439","tid":2457453,"uid":253883,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"諗下自己打一世工 都唔會買到樓<br />\n就會放鬆哂"},{"pid":"03e759d37d41d7c4008f486b34214e60aef73a42","tid":2457453,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"做運動啦<br />\n同睇多啲motivation 嘅ig post <br />\n有時會有幫你打氣感覺"},{"pid":"1623b609b892d01d35560ed2501b00da64cce1b0","tid":2457453,"uid":75356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T16:05:33.000Z","msg":"揾個興趣 將返工變成供養你嘅興趣 收工先開始生活"},{"pid":"4a373d2aaeeddd76580a866190636581a138b079","tid":2457453,"uid":323520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"92957689723a4a566a521ccba92ce03c0b9c4d9c","tid":2457453,"uid":50521,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"做運動，真係幾好，出身汗，我都一樣，但唔係公司，唔係壓力，只係個人好灰，成日都好唔開心禁，所以成日做下運動，做做下就唔會諗禁多野。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"但放工都好夜，屋企又細，有無咩係可以係屋企咁有限嘅空間做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849717a58ec9a3dfa7431221ef2de69854d0ebb4","tid":2457453,"uid":323520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf3741f6da842b965100dc0d3831781847e53439","tid":2457453,"uid":253883,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"諗下自己打一世工 